front.title: Ronto
front.gametext: May add 2 'riders' (passengers). Ability = 1/4. When 'ridden' by a Jawa, moves for free and draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise.
front.lore: Beast of burden often used by Jawas. Excellent sense of smell. Poor vision. Slow moving. Tough hide. Easily startled by fast-moving speeders.
